headline: ComEd Names Ajit Apte as SVP of Customer Operations
summary: CHICAGO, September 25, 2025--ComEd announced Ajit Apte, with more than two decades of experience in the industry and at Exelon, has been appointed to the role of senior vice president of Customer Operations. Effective earlier this month, this key appointment will position ComEd to continue to enhance the customer experience for over 9 million people served in northern Illinois.
